        <div class="verdict">⭐ Rating: 3.9/5 — Best budget-friendly option for small contractors</div>

        <p>Contractor Foreman positions itself as the affordable alternative to Buildertrend and Procore — and the pricing claim holds up. At $49/mo for the Basic plan and $299/mo for Unlimited (unlimited users, all features), it undercuts every major competitor significantly.</p>

        <p>But cheaper doesn't always mean better. This review gives you the honest picture: where Contractor Foreman delivers real value, where it cuts corners, and who it's actually right for.</p>

